---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — ToolScout" description="Privacy Policy for ToolScout">
  <article class="prose prose-invert mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: March 20, 2026</em></p>
    
    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect minimal data: standard web server logs (IP address, browser type, pages visited) and any information you voluntarily provide (e.g., email for contact).</p>
    
    <h2>2. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> — hosting provider</li>
      <li><strong>TikTok API</strong> — to display our own video performance metrics</li>
      <li><strong>Affiliate networks</strong> (Impact.com, Gumroad) — may set cookies to track referrals</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use essential cookies only. Third-party affiliate links may set their own cookies per their respective privacy policies.</p>
    
    <h2>4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Information is used solely to operate the site, improve content quality, and fulfill affiliate program requirements. We do not sell personal data.</p>
    
    <h2>5. TikTok Integration</h2>
    <p>We use TikTok's Display API to access our own account's video metrics (views, likes, shares). We do not access, store, or process any other TikTok user's data.</p>
    
    <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Server logs are retained for up to 30 days. We do not maintain user accounts or persistent user data.</p>
    
    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request deletion of any personal data we hold by contacting us. Under GDPR, EU residents have additional rights including access, rectification, and portability.</p>
    
    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>
    
    <h2>9. Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy at any time. Changes are effective upon posting.</p>
    
    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy questions? Email <a href="mailto:quarmochi.mehdi@gmail.com">quarmochi.mehdi@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
